Non-edge cases:
"Stereotypical cluster" 2 shards, 3 nodes per replicaset, authentication enabled
"Stereotypical non-shard replset" 3 nodes

Edge cases:
"Standalone-not-really" 1-node replicaset
"Batshit crazy cluster" 1 node in configsvr replset, one shard with 2 nodes and a dead node, and another shard with 3 normal nodes and a hidden node and an arbiter.

SSL support
